quran[11{c,v,t}:
7,196,mera haami o nasir woh khuda hai jis ne yeh kitaab nazil ki hai aur woh naik admion ki himayat karta hai
7,197,bakhilaf iss ke tum jinhein khuda ko chore kar pkarte ho woh nah tumhari madad kar saktay hain aur nah khud apni madad hi karne ke qabil hain
7,198,"balkay agar tum inhen seedhi raah par anay ke liye kaho to woh tumhari baat sun bhi nahi satke bzahir tum ko aisa nazar aata hai ke woh tumhari taraf dekh rahay hain magar fi al waqea woh kuch bhi nahi dekhte """
7,199,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, narmi o dar guzar ka tareeqa ikhtiyar karo, Maroof ki Talqeen kiye jao, aur jahilon se nah uljho"
7,200,"agar kabhi shetan tumhe aksaye to Allah ki panah mango, woh sab kuch suneney aur jan-nay wala hai"
7,201,haqeeqat mein jo lau g mut-taqi hain unn ka haal to yeh hota hai ke kabhi shetan ke assar se koi bura khayaal agar inhen chhoo bhi jata hai to woh foran chokannay ho jatay hain aur phir inhen saaf nazar anay lagta hai ke un ke liye sahih tareeq car kya hai
7,202,"rahay un ke ( yani shyatin ke ) bhai band, to woh inhen un ki kaj rawi mein kheinchain liye chalay jatay hain aur inhen bhataknay mein koi kasar utha nahi rakhtay"
7,203,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jab tum inn logon ke samnay koi nishani ( yani moujza ) paish nahi karte to yeh kehte hain ke tum ne apne liye koi nishani kyun nah intikhab kar li? un se kaho"" mein to sirf uss wahi ki pairwi karta hon jo mere rab ne meri taraf bhaije hai yeh baseerat ki roshniyan hain tumahray rab ki taraf se aur hadaayat aur rehmat hai unn logon ke liye jo isay qubool karen"
7,204,"jab quran tumahray samnay parha jaye to usay tavajja se suno aur khamosh raho, shayad ke tum par bhi rehmat ho jaye """
7,205,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ko subah o shaam yaad kya karo dil hi dil mein zaari aur khauf ke sath aur zabaan se bhi halki aawaz ke sath tum un logon mein se nah ho jao jo ghaflat mein parre hue hain"
7,206,"jo farishtay tumahray rab ke huzoor taqarab ka maqam rakhtay hain woh kabhi apni barayi ke ghamand mein aa kar is ki ibadat se mun nahi morty aur is ki tasbeeh karte hain, aur is ke agay jhuke rehtay hain"
